<div class="page"><header class="brand"><div class="logo">FIXFY</div><div class="meta">Getfixfy Ltd &middot; Co. No. 15406523</div></header>
  <h1 class="title">SELF-BILLING<span class="accent">AGREEMENT</span></h1>
  <p class="lead">This Self-Billing Agreement (the &ldquo;Agreement&rdquo;) is made between <span class="party">GETFIXFY LTD</span>, a company incorporated in England and Wales under company number 15406523, registered office 124 City Road, London EC1V 2NX (the &ldquo;Self-Biller&rdquo; or &ldquo;Fixfy&rdquo;), and the undersigned Partner (the &ldquo;Supplier&rdquo;).</p>
  <p class="lead">It sets out the terms on which Fixfy will issue self-billed invoices on behalf of the Supplier for Jobs completed through the Fixfy platform, in accordance with HMRC self-billing requirements.</p>

  <div class="callout"><strong>What self-billing means.</strong> Under a self-billing arrangement, the customer (Fixfy) prepares the supplier&rsquo;s invoice and sends a copy to the supplier with the payment. The Supplier agrees not to raise its own sales invoices for the transactions covered by this Agreement.</div>

  <div class="label">Supplier Details</div>
  <table class="details">
    <tr><td class="k">Full legal / Trading name</td><td class="v"></td></tr>
    <tr><td class="k">Business address</td><td class="v"></td></tr>
    <tr><td class="k">Company / UTR number (if any)</td><td class="v"></td></tr>
    <tr><td class="k">VAT registration number (if VAT registered)</td><td class="v"></td></tr>
    <tr><td class="k">Email</td><td class="v"></td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2 class="section">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;Agreement to Self-Bill</h2>
  <p><span class="sub">1.1</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;The Supplier agrees that Fixfy may issue self-billed invoices for all Jobs completed by the Supplier through the platform for the duration of this Agreement.</p>
  <p><span class="sub">1.2</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;The Supplier agrees not to raise sales invoices for the supplies covered by this Agreement.</p>
  <p><span class="sub">1.3</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;This Agreement takes effect on the date of acceptance and remains in force for a period of twelve (12) months, automatically renewing for successive twelve-month periods unless terminated earlier in accordance with clause 5.</p>

  <h2 class="section">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;Supplier Obligations</h2>
  <p>The Supplier agrees to:</p>
  <ul class="dash">
    <li>accept self-billed invoices raised by Fixfy on the Supplier&rsquo;s behalf until this Agreement ends;</li>
    <li>notify Fixfy immediately if the Supplier changes its VAT registration number;</li>
    <li>notify Fixfy immediately if the Supplier becomes, or ceases to be, registered for VAT;</li>
    <li>notify Fixfy immediately if the Supplier transfers its business, or part of it, as a going concern;</li>
    <li>not issue its own VAT or sales invoices for the supplies covered by this Agreement; and</li>
    <li>keep copies of all self-billed invoices it receives.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="section">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;Fixfy Obligations</h2>
  <p>Fixfy agrees to:</p>
  <ul class="dash">
    <li>issue self-billed invoices showing the Supplier&rsquo;s name, address and, where applicable, VAT registration number, together with all particulars required for a valid VAT invoice;</li>
    <li>include on each self-billed invoice the statement &ldquo;The VAT shown is your output tax due to HMRC&rdquo; where the Supplier is VAT registered;</li>
    <li>issue a new self-billing agreement if the Supplier&rsquo;s VAT registration number changes;</li>
    <li>send a copy of each self-billed invoice to the Supplier and retain a copy; and</li>
    <li>not reclaim input tax on invoices that are incorrect or where this Agreement has ended.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="section">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;VAT and the Agency Model</h2>
  <p><span class="sub">4.1</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;Fixfy acts as a disclosed agent introducing Jobs between Clients and the Supplier. The Supplier supplies its Services to the Client; Fixfy provides agency, coordination and platform services and charges commission.</p>
  <p><span class="sub">4.2</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;Where the Supplier is VAT registered, the self-billed invoice will reflect the VAT due on the Supplier&rsquo;s supply. Fixfy&rsquo;s commission is accounted for separately, with VAT applied to the commission as required by law.</p>
  <p><span class="sub">4.3</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;The Supplier is solely responsible for accounting to HMRC for any VAT and income tax due on its supplies.</p>

  <h2 class="section">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;Duration and Termination</h2>
  <p><span class="sub">5.1</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;Either party may terminate this Agreement at any time by written notice (including through the platform).</p>
  <p><span class="sub">5.2</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;This Agreement automatically ends if the Supplier&rsquo;s circumstances change such that self-billing is no longer permitted under HMRC rules, including a change of VAT registration number until a new agreement is made.</p>
  <p><span class="sub">5.3</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;On termination, the Supplier resumes responsibility for issuing its own invoices for subsequent supplies.</p>

  <h2 class="section">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;Governing Law</h2>
  <p><span class="sub">6.1</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;This Agreement is governed by the laws of England and Wales and operated in accordance with HMRC self-billing requirements (VAT Notice 700/62 as amended from time to time).</p>

  <div class="execution">
    <h2 class="exec">ACCEPTANCE</h2>
    <p>By clicking &ldquo;Sign&rdquo; / &ldquo;Accept&rdquo; in the Fixfy onboarding portal, or by signing below, the Supplier agrees to this Self-Billing Agreement and confirms the Supplier Details above are correct.</p>
    <div class="sigwrap">
      <div class="sigcell">
        <div class="h">GETFIXFY LTD (Self-Biller)</div>
        <div class="org">Getfixfy Ltd</div>
        <div class="org">124 City Road, London EC1V 2NX</div>
        <div class="org">Co. No. 15406523</div>
        <div class="sigline"></div><div class="sigcap">Authorised signatory</div>
        <div class="sigline"></div><div class="sigcap">Date</div>
      </div>
      <div class="sigcell">
        <div class="h">THE SUPPLIER (Partner)</div>
        <div class="org">&nbsp;</div>
        <div class="sigline"></div><div class="sigcap">Name / Business name</div>
        <div class="sigline"></div><div class="sigcap">Signature</div>
        <div class="sigline"></div><div class="sigcap">Date</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer class="foot"><span>Self-Billing Agreement &middot; v2026 &mdash; Confidential</span><span>Getfixfy Ltd</span></footer></div>',
  true
);

